 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Corrosion:

    This Pokémon's moves and item 
  ignore the usual immunity of 
  Poison and Steel Pokémon when 
  attempting to inflict poison.

  Oblivious:

    This Pokémon cannot be infatuated 
  and is immune to captivate.

  If a Pokémon is infatuated 
  and acquires this ability, its 
  infatuation is cleared.


